msgid ""
"- Check permissions: Your site's robots.txt might be blocking Instagram from"
" accessing the media folder (make sure /social_instagram is not blocked)."
msgstr ""
"- ກວດສອບການອະນຸຍາດ: ໄຟລ໌ robots.txt ຂອງເວັບໄຊເຈົ້າອາດຈະບລັອກ Instagram ບໍ່ໃຫ້ເຂົ້າເຖິງໂຟນ"
"ເດີມີເດຍ (ໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າ /social_instagram ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກບລັອກ)."

#. module: social_instagram
